STEP00
-> enable SSH on management IP

S1
---
ena
conf t
hostname S1
int vlan 1
ip add 10.1.100.1 255.255.255.0
no shut
exit
ip domain-name opensysadmins.lab
crypto key generate rsa modulus 1024
username admin priv 15 secret admin
line vty 0 4
transport input ssh
login local
end
wr

